00517 void EaglePageOperations_SendPageToProviderInteger_(EaglePageProvider *provider,
00518                                                     EaglePage *source1,
00519                                                     EaglePage *source2)
00520 {
00521     int i;
00522     EagleDataTypeIntegerType *source2data = (EagleDataTypeIntegerType*) source2->data;
00523     
00524     if(NULL == source1) {
00525         /* send all */
00526         for(i = 0; i < source2->count; ++i) {
00527             EaglePageProvider_add(provider, &source2data[i]);
00528         }
00529     }
00530     else {
00531         /* send some */
00532         EagleDataTypeIntegerType *source1data = (EagleDataTypeIntegerType*) source1->data;
